    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah the tighter lattice idea helps. what about the micronaire levels? we're trying to balance a really dense, tight weave with a very soft hand-feel. if we go too dense to achieve that \"protective\" quality you mentioned, are we going to lose the premium luxury feel that clients expect from this grade of cotton?",
